title: **FANTASTIC Lake Bde Maka Ska (Calhoun) Dean Parkway Condo for Rent**
posting_body: ['Available starting on 9/1/2022. 6 month lease option available.', 'Spacious 1 BR/1 BA upper unit overlooking beautiful Dean Parkway and Lake Bde Maka Ska (formerly Calhoun)!', 'Gleaming hardwood floors, spacious living room, lots of closets for storage, great bedroom with large closet organizer and ceiling fan, beautiful balcony overlooking Lake Calhoun and Dean Parkway, recently updated kitchen with under cabinet LED lighting and pantry cabinet with roll-outs, recently remodeled bathroom (new everything!), and recently professionally painted!', 'This condo is well-managed and includes laundry, a spacious heated corner parking stall, climate controlled storage unit, off-street guest parking spaces, on-street guest parking, and patios on both sides for grilling and entertaining.', 'I will also throw in a wood bed frame and other furniture if needed with the unit rental.', "Electricity/AC, cable (Comcast-ready), and phone are the tenant's responsibility.", 'All other utilities paid by landlord.', 'No dogs are allowed within the building.', 'Walk and bike to everything. .', '.directly', 'next to the beautiful Minneapolis Greenway!!!', 'Bus line (to downtown, UofM, etc.) is also a ½ block away.', 'Steps from the beach, tons of shopping and restaurants, Whole Foods, and the Calhoun Beach Club Athletic Center!', "This condo will rent quickly so please act fast if you're interested!", 'Annual lease / $1,795 per month / $1,795 security deposit due upon contract execution.']
